data.description: Welcome to 208 Tabby Creek Circle.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features hardwood floors, front patio, and a privacy fence in the backyard.  It is conveniently located in the highly desirable Sangaree neighborhood that has no HOA and is just minutes from Nexton Village, I-26, schools, and many other amenities.
